name: .08 THE BEST HAIR DAY FEB 12 2008 AT GRANDMA'S HOUSE (*animated). Lucky Lucy van Delft
description: In 2008 I cashed out the remainder of my 401K and went to visit my grandmother twice in one year. Needless to say there must be something in the water in east Holland because it was a silkysmooth (as in the movie zohan) curly mane never to be repeated again at this level of luxuriousness. software used to make this - free version of canva
